To install Wikidot Open Source follow the points:

1. Prepare a PostgreSQL database.

$ su postgres
# createuser --pwprompt wdowner
# createdb wd --owner wdowner
# exit

2. Fill in conf/wikidot.ini section [db].

3. Issue the following command:

$ make wikidot

4. Go to the URL make prints at the end to configure your wiki users.
